KarpReilly LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 25, 2017 5:21 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of KarpReilly LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
KarpReilly LLC is a private equity firm specializing in management buyouts, acquisition financing, recapitalizations, and growth capital investments. The firm seeks to invest in private and public, lower middle market, small and mid-sized companies. It seeks to invest in e-commerce, direct-to-consumer, consumer brands, branded consumer products, apparel, food and beverage, natural products, LOHAS (Lifestyles of Health and Sustainability), healthcare services, business services, restaurants, and retail sectors. The firm makes equity investments as small as $3 million and $5 million – and as large as $75 million per company. It seeks to co-invest in its portfolio companies. The firm acquires b...
KarpReilly LLC is a private equity firm specializing in management buyouts, acquisition financing, recapitalizations, and growth capital investments. The firm seeks to invest in private and public, lower middle market, small and mid-sized companies. It seeks to invest in e-commerce, direct-to-consumer, consumer brands, branded consumer products, apparel, food and beverage, natural products, LOHAS (Lifestyles of Health and Sustainability), healthcare services, business services, restaurants, and retail sectors. The firm makes equity investments as small as $3 million and $5 million – and as large as $75 million per company. It seeks to co-invest in its portfolio companies. The firm acquires both majority and minority stakes in its portfolio companies. It typically holds its investment for a period of eight and 10 years. KarpReilly LLC is based in Greenwich, Connecticut.
Detailed Description


104 Field Point RoadGreenwich, CT 06830United StatesFounded in 2006



Phone: 203-504-9900

www.karpreilly.com







