KarpReilly LLC Key Developments

Cafe Rio Reportedly Considering Strategic Options
May 16 17
KarpReilly LLC is reportedly working with Piper Jaffray to find a strategic option for Cafe Rio, Inc. A sale or an initial public offering are both being considered for Cafe Rio.


Hooters of America Sale Reportedly Called Off
Aug 7 15
H.I.G. Capital, LLC has called off sale of Hooters of America, Inc., sources stated. Hooters of America investors now plan to recapitalize the company and take a dividend. H.I.G and KarpReilly LLC now plan to recapitalize the company and take a dividend. They plan to revisit options, which could include a sale or IPO, the source said.


